Pacman Game

Features
🎮 Classic Pacman gameplay.
🧠 Smart AI-controlled ghosts with unique behaviors.
📈 Multiple levels with increasing difficulty.
🏆 Scoring and game-over system.
Controls
⬆⬇⬅➡ Arrow Keys: Move Pacman.
How to Play
🍒 Collect all the dots on the map to complete the level.
👻 Avoid ghosts or eat them after grabbing a power-up.
💔 The game ends when Pacman loses all lives.
Requirements
Unity Version: [Insert Unity Version Here]
Platform: Windows/Mac/Other
Installation
📂 Clone the repository or download the project folder.
🛠️ Open the project in Unity.
▶️ Build and run the game.
